arcotic analgesic.', 'Others', 'Meperidine and fentanyl should not be used with MAOIs or other agents that possess MAOI activity (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/109055/', '', 'Naltrexone, Acetaminophen, Ibuprofen, Celecoxib, Acetylsalicylic acid, Naloxone', 'Pertuzumab, Olaparib, Bortezomib, Tisagenlecleucel, Aminolevulinic acid, Omacetaxine mepesuccinate, Tazemetostat, Altretamine, Tagraxofusp, Pegaspargase, Ixazomib, More', 1767369485);
