cotic analgesic.', 'Others', 'Meperidine and fentanyl should not be used with MAOIs or other agents that possess MAOI activity (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/109071/', '', 'Naltrexone, Acetaminophen, Ibuprofen, Celecoxib, Acetylsalicylic acid, Naloxone', 'Amantadine', 1767369485);
